snippet.title: The Legend of Bum-bo Coming to Switch/PS5/Xbox on June 29
snippet.description: The prequel to The Binding of Isaac, The Legend of Bum-bo is coming to Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X/S on June 29, 2022! Wishlist now: https://bit.ly/Bum-bo_Switch  https://bit.ly/Bum-bo_PS5  https://bit.ly/Bum-bo_Xbox
